_sText:
This map for CSS, depicts a warehouse in a secret facility, belonging to the Dominion Force (a made up military unit). Comes complete with *.nav file. Terrorists, have broken into the warehouse from the main doors. CT's begin in the storeroom. The fully laden warehouse, full of boxes, crates and other junk, stand in the way. Last person/s standing are the victor/s.

Special thanks to Vortex, for playtesting it for me.

dAVROs
